er而闻名，也宣布了本月活动的结束。上个月，Yuketsu Akatsuki宣布最后一项活动也结束了。 </p><div class="mg-mogura-card m-0 mb-2 mb-md-3"><div class="d-flex"><div class="mg-mogura-card-thumb position-relative"><img class="mg-img-cover position-absolute h-100 w-100" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2019/04/ed3d6a3fa5533f79bdb5649526b578ec-kix.yzzlxm16w4vw-300x150.webp"></div><div class="card-body mg-card-text p-2 p-lg-3"><h3 class="h6 mt-0 mw-0 mb-1 p-0 card-title mg-card-title mg-text-break-all text-dark font-weight-normal"> “ Livari” Vtuber Yuni Akatsuki将于10月31日结束活动</h3><div class="text-gray mg-mogura-card-excerpt mb-1 my-md-2">属于人才办公室“ Live Livari”的Vtuber，Yuni Akatsuki和Memori Mori宣布，他们将于10月31日结束活动。 Yuni Akatsuki于2018年4月18日，Memori Mizumori于2023年2月13日首次推销[...</div> <span class="badge badge-outline-live mg-mogura-card-badge px-2">VTUBER</span> <span class="text-muted small ml-1">2023.10.26</span></div></div></div><p> （参考）<a href="https://twitter.com/Liverary_JP/status/1730183642352357540" target="_blank" rel="noopener">x帐户</a></p><p>Live Livari Vtuber Mochizuki <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Himari</a>邮报<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/himarimochimoon-activity-ended/">是活动的终结</a>。</p> ;
